{"parse":{"title":"Entertainment Software Rating Association","pageid":24285593,"revid":858680815,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption class=\"fn org\">Entertainment Software Rating Association (ESRA)</caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"logo\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/File:ESAR_Final_28_logo.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"ESAR Final 28 logo.png\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a7/ESAR_Final_28_logo.png/220px-ESAR_Final_28_logo.png\" width=\"220\" height=\"138\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a7/ESAR_Final_28_logo.png/330px-ESAR_Final_28_logo.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a7/ESAR_Final_28_logo.png/440px-ESAR_Final_28_logo.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1748\" data-file-height=\"1099\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_business_entities\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"List of business entities\">Type</a></div></th><td class=\"category\" style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\nSelf-regulatory</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Industry</th><td class=\"category\" style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Video_game_content_rating_system\" title=\"Video game content rating system\">Organization and rating system</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Founded</th><td style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n2007 in <a href=\"/wiki/Islamic_Republic_of_Iran\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Islamic Republic of Iran\">Islamic Republic of Iran</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Headquarters</th><td class=\"label\" style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Tehran\" title=\"Tehran\">Tehran</a>, Iran</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Area served</div></th><td style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\nIran</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Key people</div></th><td class=\"agent\" style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<p>Reza Ahmadi<br />(<span style=\"font-size:85%;\"><a href=\"/wiki/President_(corporate_title)\" title=\"President (corporate title)\">President</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/CEO\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"CEO\">CEO</a></span>)\n</p>\nSeyed Mohammad Ali Seyed Hosseini<br />(<span style=\"font-size:85%;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Entrepreneur\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Entrepreneur\">Founder</a></span>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" style=\"padding-right:0.5em;\">Website</th><td style=\"line-height:1.35em;\">\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://en.ircg.ir/service/3%7C\">www.esra.org</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:ESRAOfficial_Logo.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d7/ESRAOfficial_Logo.png/220px-ESRAOfficial_Logo.png\" width=\"220\" height=\"82\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d7/ESRAOfficial_Logo.png/330px-ESRAOfficial_Logo.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d7/ESRAOfficial_Logo.png/440px-ESRAOfficial_Logo.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"515\" data-file-height=\"193\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:ESRAOfficial_Logo.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>former logo</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Entertainment Software Rating Association</b> (<b>ESRA</b>)<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a <a href=\"/wiki/Self-regulatory_organization\" title=\"Self-regulatory organization\">self-regulatory organization</a> that assigns age and content ratings in <a href=\"/wiki/Iran\" title=\"Iran\">Iran</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> The system was established in 2007 by the <a href=\"/wiki/Iran_Computer_and_Video_Games_Foundation\" title=\"Iran Computer and Video Games Foundation\">Iran National Foundation of Computer Games</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> and has the status of a <a href=\"/wiki/Research_project\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Research project\">research project</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Entertainment_Software_Rating_Association&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Alexander, Leigh. <a re